  "excerpt": "The Fukutake Foundation has opened the Tadao Ando-designed Naoshima New Museum of Art in Japan. The museum is the latest addition to the Benesse Art Site Naoshima, a decades-long cultural initiative integrating art, architecture, and nature across the islands of Naoshima, Teshima, and Inujima...",
