  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/de/dee0dc2e5a2137301ac6cbdf6423f84d.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image credit: GION\" data-size=\"1800x1199\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/de/dee0dc2e5a2137301ac6cbdf6423f84d.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/de/dee0dc2e5a2137301ac6cbdf6423f84d.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/de/dee0dc2e5a2137301ac6cbdf6423f84d.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/de/dee0dc2e5a2137301ac6cbdf6423f84d.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image credit: GION\" alt=\"Image credit: GION\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage credit: GION\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThe Fukutake Foundation has opened the \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/99728/tadao-ando\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTadao Ando\u003c/a\u003e-designed \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/article/150455869/tadao-ando-s-naoshima-new-museum-of-art-to-open-in-early-2025\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNaoshima New Museum of Art\u003c/a\u003e in Japan. The museum is the latest addition to the Benesse Art Site Naoshima, a decades-long cultural initiative integrating art, architecture, and nature across the islands of \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/16095/naoshima\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eNaoshima\u003c/a\u003e, Teshima, and Inujima in \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/336/japan\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eJapan’s\u003c/a\u003e Seto Inland Sea.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/20/20a4230e9612896b4346a15e43b7162c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x770\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/20/20a4230e9612896b4346a15e43b7162c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/20/20a4230e9612896b4346a15e43b7162c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/20/20a4230e9612896b4346a15e43b7162c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/20/20a4230e9612896b4346a15e43b7162c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage credit: GION\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/70/70511af5ad568195de1d9172c284f7d2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x770\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/70/70511af5ad568195de1d9172c284f7d2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/70/70511af5ad568195de1d9172c284f7d2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/70/70511af5ad568195de1d9172c284f7d2.jpg?auto=compress%2Cfo